oesn't exhaust me."],[2677,2802,"That's none of your business."],[4254,4412,"There's only one event left for today."],[4462,4537,"Looks like you're taking home"],[4537,4612,"another gold medal."],[4871,4996,"Bro, we just won the championship."],[5038,5134,"Why are you so upset?"],[5163,5397,"Even you can tell that I'm pissed."],[5451,5601,"Only that dummy can't."],[5630,5726,"Who's the dummy?"],[5918,6026,"Are you talking about Hazel?"],[6072,6177,"Did you guys get into a fight?"],[6206,6318,"She didn't give me the chance"],[6318,6535,"to argue with her."],[6606,6660,"Bro..."],[6794,6844,"So you're telling me"],[6844,6973,"you're actually into Hazel?"],[7044,7148,"This isn't about Zoe?"],[7332,7432,"Bro, I'm not gonna lie,"],[7432,7553,"but if I were Hazel,"],[7640,7749,"I wouldn't choose you either."],[7778,7937,"Every time you have to choose"],[7937,8049,"between her and Zoe,"],[8070,8162,"you choose Zoe."],[8208,8358,"How is she supposed to know you like her?"],[8491,8641,"Well, I can't marry you, can I?"],[8679,8833,"Because you're engaged to Zoe."],[8883,9013,"Because I agreed to marry you,"],[9013,9150,"but don't forget our arrangement."],[9150,9359,"You stay out of my life."],[9367,9488,"Marcus, I don't want you to go."],[9488,9701,"I promise I'll be right back."],[9713,9793,"Hazel,"],[9793,9993,"I've been chasing you around all day."],[9993,10151,"Do you really not know what I want?"],[10151,10206,"So what?"],[10260,10364,"Should I be flattered?"],[10406,10523,"So she can't..."],[10677,10794,"feel my love for her?"]],"44":[[58,104,"Marcus,"],[104,204,"is there anything you'd like to say"],[204,287,"to the audience?"],[563,625,"Alright, it's getting late."],[625,750,"Let's head back to the hotel, yeah?"],[750,800,"Okay."],[950,1255,"Hazel, everything was my fault."],[1255,1476,"Please, don't be mad at me."],[1526,1614,"Who's Hazel?"],[1885,2143,"Hazel, I know you can hear me."],[2369,2452,"I love you."],[2523,2727,"Haven't you learned anything, Hazel?"],[2761